#compdef eventlircd
# Documentation: (no Debian/Ubuntu manpage in catalog; upstream at github.com/eventlircd/eventlircd)
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-16
# Verified: no upstream manpage retrievable. Tool kept per "do not delete
